nov vjovanov  4096 May  4 16:48 human-intervention-logs\ndrwxrwxr-x 404 vjovanov vjovanov 20480 May  4 16:33 metadata\n-rw-rw-r--   1 vjovanov vjovanov   385 May  4 16:33 settings.gradle\ndrwxrwxr-x  11 vjovanov vjovanov  4096 May  4 16:33 skills\ndrwxrwxr-x 398 vjovanov vjovanov 20480 May  4 16:33 stats\ndrwxrwxr-x   5 vjovanov vjovanov  4096 May  4 16:33 tests\nrg: logs/io.github.pdvrieze.xmlutil:serialization-jvm:0.91.3: IO error for operation on logs/io.github.pdvrieze.xmlutil:serialization-jvm:0.91.3: No such file or directory (os error 2)\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
